==English==
===Etymology===
Middle English, from Middle Dutch from Middle Low German from Old High German ''[[stuba]]''
===Noun===
'''stove'''

# a [[heater]], a closed apparatus to burn fuel for the warming of a room 
# a [[device]] for [[heat]]ing [[food]], (''UK'') a [[cooker]]

